nodes.text: A male individual from the planet Coruscant was the third husband of the Republic Army officer Elin Garza. The two were married sometime after her previous husband Joron Tal'vor's death in 3671 BBY during the Great Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire, but their marriage was later annulled. The name of Garza's husband was also classified under what her fellows considered mysterious circumstances.
Elin Garza's husband was first mentioned in the 2012 reference guide Star Wars: The Old Republic Encyclopedia's entry for Garza, though his species was not identified.
